		// Short-lived timer that reasserts the cursor every tick while a
		// mouse button is held down. Without this, NT resets the cursor to
		// its default on click and the hand cursor blinks off until the
		// next MouseMove (or MouseUp, which is the final reassert). The
		// timer fires fast enough (~16ms) that the cursor never visibly
